### What does this PR do?

Enhance the border radius for the heatmap, for more info plz go to [issue](https://github.com/apache/echarts/issues/16490).

## View

### Before

<img width="784" alt="image" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20939839/153812505-a77784a0-b81c-4c46-a64e-7145c43c1cb0.png">

### After

<img width="1440" alt="image" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20939839/153812390-72ad1145-9754-4730-b7e8-d17c4e0fabd7.png">

Also, you can use it in the Calendar Heatmap.

<img width="1440" alt="image" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20939839/153815510-320464e2-7476-4cc3-94a3-c19a319e6730.png">

#### How to use it

`borderRadius`: `number || number[]`

more info plz go to [zrender.Rect opts.shape.r](https://ecomfe.github.io/zrender-doc/public/api.html#zrenderrect)

```js
option = {
    series: {
        // ...
        itemStyle: {
            // borderRadius: 10,
            borderRadius: [10, 20, 30, 40],
        }
    }
}
```

Also, you can custom set it by data from each item.
```js
var data = [
    {
        itemStyle: {
            borderRadius: [10, 20],
        },
        value: [0, 0, 5]
    },
    {
        itemStyle: {
            borderRadius: [30, 40],
        },
        value: [1, 1, 7]
    }
]

option = {
    // ...
    series: [{
        // ...
        data,
        // ...
    }]
}
```

